thread.title: Kaye

author: Kaye
title: Kaye
text: From the time I interviewed John Cataldo, a Partner of Nelson Alexander Pascoe Vale, and engaged him as the Real Estate Agent to manage the sale of my late Mother's home he was very impressive. John's professionalism and experience, together with his humility, is second to none. He always kept me fully informed during the sale process and worked diligently to achieve a successful outcome, always showing a great deal of respect. I have no hesitation in recommending John Cataldo as a unique and outstanding Real Estate Agent.
